       8/10 DVD

On this scale, this upload is about 4-6/10.

I threw this together in the last week or 2 after I realized that it would be a good way to start uploading documentaries.
Stephen Hawking's Universe (2010) and Stephen Hawking and the Theory of Everything (2008) are here as Into the Universe (2010) and Master of the Universe (2008) respectively (those 2 former names are just renamed releases of those miniseries in other countries).  Beyond the Horizon (2009) is not here because I didn’t find it.

These copies are drawn from the highest quality sources possible, but they are encoded with lower bitrates at 360p resolution to make them ideal for the small screen - phones, tablets, laptops, and monitors.
Keep seeding so I can focus on seeding the next upload!
